\c 17
\s Izikhubekiso, ukuthethelelana, ukholo
\p
\v 1 Wasesithi kubafundi\x + 17.1,2, Mat. 18.7,6.\x*: Kakungeke kwenzeke ukuthi kungaveli izikhubekiso; kodwa maye \add kulowo\add* ezivela ngaye\x + 13.33.\x*!
\v 2 Kungaba ngcono kuye ukuthi ilitshe lokuchola elikhulu ligaxwe entanyeni yakhe, abesephoselwa olwandle\x + Mark. 9.42.\x*, kulokuthi akhubekise abe munye kulaba abancinyane\x + 17.1,2. Mat. 18.7,6.\x*.
\v 3 Zinanzeleleni lina\x + 12.1. 21.34. Seb. 5.35. 20.28.\x*.
\p Njalo nxa umfowenu ekona\x + Mat. 18.15.\x*, mkhuze\x + 2 Tim. 4.2.\x*; futhi nxa ephenduka, mthethelele.
\v 4 Njalo loba ekona kuze kube kasikhombisa ngosuku, abesebuya kuwe kasikhombisa ngosuku, esithi: Ngiyaphenduka; uzamthethelela\x + Mat. 18.21.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Abaphostoli basebesithi eNkosini\x + 9.10. Mark. 6.30.\x*: Yandisa kithi ukholo\x + Mark. 9.24.\x*.
\v 6 INkosi yasisithi: Uba lilokholo olungangohlamvu lwemasitedi\x + Mat. 17.20. 21.21.Mark. 11.23.Mark. 9.23.\x*, belingatsho kulesisihlahla somabhulosi \add ukuthi\add*: Quphuka, ugxumekeke olwandle; futhi besizalilalela\x + 19.4. Mat. 17.20.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Kodwa nguwuphi kini olenceku elimayo kumbe eyelusayo, ohle athi kiyo ingena ivela ensimini\x + 21.9. Mat. 13.21.\x*: Sondela, uhlale ekudleni?
\v 8 Kodwa kazukutsho yini kuyo \add ukuthi\add*: Lungisa engingakudla\x + 12.37.\x*, uzibhince\x + 12.37.\x* ungincedise, ngize ngidle nginathe; njalo emva kwalokhu udle unathe wena\x + 12.37.\x*?
\v 9 Uyayibonga yini leyonceku, ngoba yenze izinto ezilayiweyo? Angicabangi.
\v 10 Kunjalo-ke lani, nxa selikwenzile konke elikulayiweyo, kalibokuthi: Sizinceku ezingasizi lutho, ngoba senze lokhu ebesifanele ukukwenza\x + Mat. 25.30. Roma 3.12. Filim. 1.11. Jobe 22.3.\x*.
\s Ukusiliswa kwamalephero alitshumi
\p
\v 11 Kwasekusithi esahamba esiya eJerusalema\x + 13.22.\x*, yena wadabula phakathi laphakathi kweSamariya\x + Joha. 4.4.\x* leGalili\x + Mat. 19.1.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Esangena emzaneni othile, amadoda alitshumi alobulephero amhlangabeza, ema khatshana\x + Levi 13.46.\x*;
\v 13 wona asephakamisa ilizwi, esithi: Jesu, Nkosi, sihawukele\x + 5.5.\x*!
\v 14 Futhi kuthe e\add wa\add*bona wathi kuwo: Hambani liyeziveza kubapristi\x + Levi 14.2. Mat. 8.4.\x*. Kwasekusithi ekusukeni kwawo, ahlanjululwa.
\v 15 Futhi omunye wawo, esebonile ukuthi usilisiwe, wabuyela, edumisa uNkulunkulu ngelizwi elikhulu\x + Mat. 15.31.\x*;
\v 16 wasesiwa ngobuso enyaweni zakhe\x + 1 Kor. 14.25.\x*, embonga; njalo yena wayengumSamariya\x + 17.11. Mat. 10.5.\x*.
\v 17 Kodwa uJesu waphendula wathi: Kakuhlanjululwanga yini abalitshumi? Bangaphi pho abayisificamunwemunye?
\v 18 Akuficakalanga ababuya ukunika uNkulunkulu udumo, ngaphandle kwalo owezizweni\x + 2 Kho. 17.24.\x*.
\v 19 Wasesithi kuye: Sukuma uhambe; ukholo lwakho\x + Mat. 9.2.\x* lukusindisile\x + Mark. 10.52.\x*.
\s Umbuso kaNkulunkulu. Ukubuya kweNdodana yomuntu
\p
\v 20 Kwathi ebuzwa ngabaFarisi, ukuthi umbuso kaNkulunkulu uzakuza nini\x + 19.11. Seb. 1.6.\x*, wasebaphendula wathi: Umbuso kaNkulunkulu kawuzi ngokukhanyayo\x + 14.1.\x*;
\v 21 njalo kabayikutsho \add ukuthi\add*: Khangelani nanku, kumbe: Khangelani nankuya. Ngoba khangelani, umbuso kaNkulunkulu uphakathi kwenu\x + 12.20. 17.23.\x*.
\p
\v 22 Wasesithi kubafundi: Kuzafika insuku lapho elizafisa\x + Mat. 9.15. Mark. 2.20. Luka 5.35. Joha. 7.34.\x* ukubona lube lunye lwezinsuku zeNdodana yomuntu, kodwa kaliyiku\add lu\add*bona\x + Joha. 8.56.\x*.
\v 23 Njalo bazakuthi kini\x + Mat. 24.23. Mark. 13.21. Luka 21.8.\x*: Khangelani nangu, kumbe: Khangelani nanguya; lingayi, njalo lingalandeli\x + 12.20. 17.23.\x*.
\v 24 Ngoba njengombane ophazimayo ukhanyisa kusukela kokunye \add ukucina\add* ngaphansi kwezulu kusiya kokunye \add ukucina\add* ngaphansi kwezulu\x + Mat. 24.27.\x*, izakuba njalo leNdodana yomuntu osukwini lwayo\x + 1 Kor. 3.13. 4. 3. 5.5. 1 Thes. 5.2. 2 Thes. 2.2. Heb. 10.25. 2 Pet. 3.10.\x*.
\v 25 Kodwa kuqala imele ihlupheke izinto ezinengi njalo ilahlwe yilesisizukulwana\x + Mark. 8.31. Luka 9.22.\x*.
\v 26 Futhi njengoba kwenzeka ensukwini zikaNowa, kuzakuba njalo lensukwini zeNdodana yomuntu.
\v 27 Babesidla, benatha, bethatha, besendiswa, kwaze kwaba lusuku uNowa angena ngalo emkhunjini, kwasekufika uzamcolo, wababhubhisa bonke\x + 17.26,27, Mat. 24.37-39.\x*.
\v 28 Ngokufananayo futhi njengoba kwenzeka ensukwini zikaLothi; babesidla, benatha, bethenga, bethengisa, behlanyela, besakha;
\v 29 kodwa ngosuku uLothi aphuma ngalo eSodoma, kwana umlilo lesibabule kuvela ezulwini, kwababhubhisa bonke\x + Gen. 19.16,24.\x*;
\v 30 kuzakuba njalo ngosuku ezakwembulwa ngalo iNdodana yomuntu\x + 1 Kor. 1.7. 2 Thes. 1.7. 1 Pet. 1.7.\x*.
\v 31 Ngalolosuku, lowo ophezu kophahla lwendlu\x + Mat. 24.17,18. Mark. 13.15,16. Luka 21.21.\x*, lempahla zakhe zisendlini, angehli uku\add ya\add*zithatha; losensimini ngokunjalo angabuyeli ezintweni ezisemuva.
\v 32 Khumbulani umkaLothi\x + Gen. 19.26.\x*.
\v 33 Loba ngubani odinga ukusindisa impilo yakhe izamlahlekela\x + Mat. 10.39.\x*; kodwa loba ngubani olahlekelwa yiyo uzayilondoloza\x + Seb. 7.19.\x*.
\v 34 Ngithi kini: Ngalobobusuku kuzakuba khona ababili embhedeni munye; omunye uzasuswa, lomunye atshiywe.
\v 35 Kuzakuba khona \add abesifazana\add* ababili bechola ndawonye; omunye uzasuswa, lomunye atshiywe\x + Mat. 24.41.\x*.
\v 36 Kuzakuba khona ababili ensimini; omunye uzasuswa, lomunye atshiywe\x + Mat. 24.40.\x*.
\v 37 Basebephendula bathi kuye: Ngaphi, Nkosi? Wasesithi kubo: Lapho okukhona isidumbu, \add ku\add*lapho amanqe azabuthana khona\x + Mat. 24.28. Jobe 39.30.\x*.
